The Story Of My Life

Hello, I am originally from South Korea but i am half Korean and Filipino. Therefore, i had to fly back and forth from Korea to Phillippines every other year to visit my family and attend the schools in both countries. Living in both of those countries was fun and exciting as i had a lot of friends. However, when i was 11, i was announced by my mom that i had to move to U.K because she was married to a British man. At first, i was scared and worried as i had to leave my friends behind. Furthermore, i had to give up my dream of being a kpop idol as i would have less opportunities if i lived in U.K. Nevertheless, after being here for 10 years now, i am happy that i moved here because the lifestyle seems a lot better and i have built up a lot of confidence. So, i guess everything really happens for a reason and i cant wait to see how my life leads to.

) } export default SinglePost
